reviewText: Really funny movie glad I bought it.
litterally ordered this movie just to hear horse D**K .MPEG's songs.
Funny, not PC which is why it's so funny. Kinda sophomoric, but it made this older guy laugh!!

One of my top comedy favorites. Definitely a movie for every man cave. Very underrated. Great story line, great dialogue and characters. Craig Robinson of Office fame is priceless as a high school dropout successful rap star whose stage name is "Horsedick.mpeg" and insists on people calling him that...and corrects anyone who leaves off the .mpeg , hilarious.
